Rails 3 App to post personal nightly dreams.
Practice Rails 3 Way

using web-app-theme, BCrypt

To Do:
	oauth
	ajax
	allow user to upload pic that best describes dream
	jquery
	pagination
	cucumber testing

===========================================================================
rails generate scaffold Dream time:datetime category:string dream:text

  rails g controller users new
  rails g model user email:string password_hash:string password_salt:string
  rake db:migrate
  rails dbconsole
  rails g controller sessions new


---
web app theme
rails g web_app_theme:theme
rails g web_app_theme:theme admin --theme="drastic-dark"
